cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS 

The paper presents a framework for robust anomaly detection in the presence of unreliable anomaly labels. It involves classification algorithms and on-line learning, which are commonly associated with machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use cases mentioned in the paper include IoT attacks (cs.CR), cloud task failures (cs.DS), and face recognition (cs.CV). Therefore, these sub-categories are also likely.
